{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "12", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "13", "M": "48", "S": "51"}}, "news": [{"title": "NCLT allows withdrawal of insolvency proceedings against Nobility Estates", "para": "The NCLT has allowed withdrawal of insolvency proceedings against Nobility Estates, developer of ATS Group\u2019s Le Grandiose project in Noida, after lenders and the erstwhile management reached a settlement. The tribunal noted that the withdrawal proposal received 92.52% approval from the committee of creditors, including votes from 636 homebuyers, and directed restoration of management control to the company\u2019s board.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/nclt-approves-withdrawal-of-insolvency-proceedings-for-nobility-estates-after-key-settlement/131039740?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-82066/131039740.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Berger Paints' net profit declines 4.63% to \u20b91,128.02 crore in FY26", "para": "Berger Paints saw its net profit dip by 4.63% in FY26. The company's total income grew by 2.99%. In the fourth quarter, profit after tax surged by 27.52%. Price increases are expected to support margins. The board recommended a dividend of \u20b94 per share.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/paints/berger-paints-reports-463-drop-in-net-profit-for-fy26/131037350?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-38830/131037350.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "paints"}, {"title": "Welspun One leases 65,000 sq ft at JNPA SEZ to Balmer Lawrie", "para": "Welspun One has entered into a letter of intent with Balmer Lawrie & Co. for 65,000 sq ft of grade A warehousing space at WTC Nhava Sheva, expected to be operational by early 2027. This strategic move will enhance Balmer La